<P>Together with a LETTER <HI>CONCERNING</HI> The Extent of INDOSTAN, the <HI>Circulation</HI> of the Gold and Silver at la&s;t &s;wallow'd up there; the <HI>Riches, Forces, Ju&s;tice,</HI> and the <HI>Principal Cau&s;e</HI> of the <HI>Decay</HI> of the STATES of <HI>ASIA.</HI></P>
